#third-party connection pooling libraries
  -c3p0, proxool, dbcp, hikari cp

How many ways a connection external resource can be acquired in hibernate application?
There are 3 fixed ways in which hibernate can aquire the external resource connection
1. jdbc approach
2. jndi datasource approach
3. connection-pool third-party libraries (c3p0, proxool)



BlazeCloudConnectionPool library
  - aws
  - oci
